WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.620 --> 00:00:03.800
Ushbu amaliyotning qolgan qismi 
uchun siz ba’zi ilovalarni yaratasiz.

00:00:03.800 --> 00:00:06.250
Siz men bilan dastur orqali basketbol 
hisobini aniqlash bo‘yicha ishlaysiz 

00:00:06.250 --> 00:00:09.380
va shunda o‘z mahoratingizni biroz 
oshirmoqchi bo‘lsangiz, sizga bir nechta 

00:00:09.380 --> 00:00:10.240
qo‘shimcha dasturlarni taqdim etamiz.

00:00:11.445 --> 00:00:13.390
Yaxshi, basketbol gollarining 
hisobi haqida ilova.

00:00:13.390 --> 00:00:15.210
Ushbu ilova "Maydon hisoblagichi" deb nomlanadi

00:00:15.210 --> 00:00:19.360
va ushbu ilovaning maqsadi basketbol 
o‘yinidagi hisobni nazorat qilishdir.

00:00:19.360 --> 00:00:23.030
U oxiridaa bunday ko‘rinishga ega bo‘lishadi, 
ammo uni bosqichma-bosqich quriladi.

00:00:23.030 --> 00:00:26.840
Sportga unchalik qiziqmaydigan xalqaro 
auditoriyamiz uchun 

00:00:26.840 --> 00:00:29.350
men gol urish va basketbol qanday 
ishlashini tushuntirib beraman.

00:00:30.390 --> 00:00:33.100
Ochko olishning birinchi usuli savat 
atrofida aylanaga teng bo‘lgan 

00:00:33.100 --> 00:00:35.150
3 talik chizig‘ida bo‘ladi.

00:00:35.150 --> 00:00:37.750
Bu ochko to‘plashning eng keng tarqalgan 
usulidir va bu ikki ochkoga yuradi.

00:00:39.010 --> 00:00:42.350
Savatga tushirishning ikkinchi 
usuli - uchta chiziq orqasidagi

00:00:42.350 --> 00:00:43.530
yana bir chiziq.

00:00:44.830 --> 00:00:47.290
Bu biroz qiyinroq, ammo sizga uch ochko beradi.

00:00:48.490 --> 00:00:50.860
Va nihoyat, jamoa to‘p kirita oladigan 
oxirgi usul 

00:00:50.860 --> 00:00:52.360
bu erkin to‘p tashlash deb ataladi.

00:00:52.360 --> 00:00:56.830
Agar o‘yinchiga zarba berishda zarbalar berilsa, 
ular erkin to‘p tashlash chizig‘ining 

00:00:56.830 --> 00:01:01.000
orqasida bitta bo‘sh savatga tushirishga 
harakat qilishadi, ammo o‘yinchilar ikkala 

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:05.489
tomonning qatoriga turishadi, lekin 
hech kim uni bu savatga tushirishga xalaqit bermaydi.

00:01:05.489 --> 00:01:07.020
Erkin otish bir ochkoga yuradi.

00:01:08.150 --> 00:01:11.880
"Maydon hisoblagichi" ilovasida siz A va B 
guruhlari bor ekanligini ko‘rishingiz mumkin.

00:01:11.880 --> 00:01:16.270
Shuningdek, sizda uch, ikkita yoki bitta 
erkin otish nuqtasini berish imkoniyati mavjud.

00:01:16.270 --> 00:01:19.150
Agar siz mukofotlash tugmachasini bossangiz
guruh ochkolarini ko‘rasiz. 

00:01:21.380 --> 00:01:23.740
O’yinni tugatishni xohlasangiz 
reset - qayta tiklash tugmachasini bosasiz.

00:01:25.135 --> 00:01:27.070
Xo‘sh, buni boshlash uchun 
biz yangi dastur yaratamiz.

00:01:27.070 --> 00:01:30.090
Siz oldinroq buni bir necha bor 
amalga oshirgansiz, shuning uchun 

00:01:30.090 --> 00:01:32.530
men sizga yangi ilovangizni yaratish uchun 
bajarishingiz kerak bo‘lgan asosiy ishlarni ko‘rsataman.

00:01:32.530 --> 00:01:35.240
Maydon hisoblagichi yangi ilovani 
chaqirganingizda unga tegishli 

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:37.280
kompaniya domenini berganingizga 
ishonch hosil qiling.

